MooseX-Deprecated
=================

Created:      2013-10-29
Home page:    <https://metacpan.org/release/MooseX-Deprecated>
Bug tracker:  <http://rt.cpan.org/Dist/Display.html?Queue=MooseX-Deprecated>
Maintainer:   Toby Inkster (TOBYINK) <tobyink@cpan.org>

0.003	2013-10-29

 [ Bug Fixes ]
 - Stop relying on warnings::fatal_enabled() function which doesn't exist
   on Perl < 5.12.

 [ Other ]
 - Make the undocumented E* functions handle the sprintf stuff within
   themselves.

0.002	2013-10-29

 - Saner technique for skipping internals when issuing warnings (and also
   when detecting the currently enabled warning categories).

0.001	2013-10-29	Initial release
